snippet.title: ESF: Final - Vegeta's Improved Transformation Hair Transition (QHD)
snippet.description:
Video is part of: "YES.. WE ARE STILL ALIVE  NEWS!" at:  https://forum.esforces.com/threads/yes-we-are-still-alive.158687

Dalte improved the hair transition from normal to Super Saiyan in his transformation sequence. The amount of flying debris (rocks) is still a work in progress, so this might change later on. 

This video is also recorded in 1440p (QHD). Any "lag" you might encounter during the video is caused by increased resolution.
